{"tid":1129504,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"美國新聞周刊《Newsweek》相隔十年再發表「世界尊敬的100名日本人」排行榜 貞子、蒼井空榜上有名","createTime":"2019-04-28T13:24:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-28T13:52:42.000Z","uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b8e124700465db8c7e1354eefcc2c7457cddbf09","tid":1129504,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T13:24:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/1556439850-f7fe72a947eb31b96a671a6d71a2dcfe-696x928.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F1556439850-f7fe72a947eb31b96a671a6d71a2dcfe-696x928.jpg&h=5cee5a31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲最新一期《Newsweek》日本版的封面，有鈴木一朗、羽生結弦、渡邊直美、中滿泉及伊藤比呂美等人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/1556440013-8e1c6ca5d0828c6a72c57036367147f9-696x486.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F1556440013-8e1c6ca5d0828c6a72c57036367147f9-696x486.jpg&h=6e128914&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲《Newsweek》日文版相隔十年再度發表「世界尊敬的百大日本人」排行榜。<br />\n<br />\n美國著名新聞周刊《Newsweek》日文版最新一期4月30日號，相隔十年再度發表「世界尊敬的百大日本人」排行榜，選出了10年來最受矚目、影響力的日本天才、鬼才及異才，除了大家熟知的大聯盟球員鈴木一朗、花式滑冰選手羽生結弦、搞笑藝人渡邊直美外，最令人意外的，莫過於因為電影《七夜怪談》爆紅，號稱恐怖片經典女王－貞子。有趣的是，報道引述「貞子」表示，對於得獎感到十分榮幸。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/1556439568-8cae0f21090fa98cebff16bed77d6054-696x464.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F1556439568-8cae0f21090fa98cebff16bed77d6054-696x464.jpg&h=358a7d8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲日本花式滑冰選手羽生結弦及搞笑藝人渡邊直美獲選為「世界尊敬的百大日本人」。<br />\n<br />\n1998年推出的《七夜怪談》掀起日本恐怖片熱潮，片中女鬼「貞子」緩慢地爬出電視機，營造出的詭異感讓膽小觀眾頭皮發麻，也因此紅遍全世界。2002年開拍好萊塢版《七夜怪談西洋篇》同樣票房豐收，讓貞子成為全世界最紅的日本女鬼，也因此在選「世界尊敬的百大日本人」中，貞子也榜上有名。報道引述「貞子」表示，對於得獎感到十分榮幸，並表示慶幸自己當初有爬出電視機，才有機會讓大家認識她，並向編劇鈴木光司的及導演中田秀夫致謝。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/1556439387-4483ab821ccb68b7fbf799d2bd78f320-696x449.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F1556439387-4483ab821ccb68b7fbf799d2bd78f320-696x449.jpg&h=14e416c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲1998年爆紅的《七夜怪談》，片中女鬼貞子獲選為「世界尊敬的百大日本人」。<br />\n<br />\n其他獲選人物還有「世界球后」大坂直美、藝術家草間彌生、《名偵探柯南》漫畫家青山剛昌、虛擬偶像Youtuber絆愛、詩人伊藤比呂美等人，知名前AV女優蒼井空也入選，充份展現這份名單的多樣性。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/1556439716-b9840e10a692e5d4253b85d4f857dcb9-696x696.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F1556439716-b9840e10a692e5d4253b85d4f857dcb9-696x696.jpg&h=8e41415d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲蒼井空。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://file.artemperor.tw/images/datas/000/025/123/6l23ie601srlcbwpfb6dqcuaga94tp3v_1400x800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile.artemperor.tw%2Fimages%2Fdatas%2F000%2F025%2F123%2F6l23ie601srlcbwpfb6dqcuaga94tp3v_1400x800.jpg&h=ca3bafd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲草間彌生。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/sports/page/800/2019/03/24/phpb7HzaL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fsports%2Fpage%2F800%2F2019%2F03%2F24%2Fphpb7HzaL.jpg&h=188711b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲大坂直美。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/28950953_932095780304550_7301305375842200676_n.jpg?_nc_cat=105&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;oh=2aef6eabb1e3cbb9311b77aa3f5ab007&amp;oe=5D2AF8AD\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F28950953_932095780304550_7301305375842200676_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D105%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26oh%3D2aef6eabb1e3cbb9311b77aa3f5ab007%26oe%3D5D2AF8AD&h=87138712&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲朱千雪。"},{"pid":"ae27f2794b1e9c7fd7a4621816210971222756be","tid":1129504,"uid":94935,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T13:51:30.000Z","msg":"日本人好尊重三文魚"},{"pid":"5e5a7106ec26f05bf601dc71041d47fb2bd21d3b","tid":1129504,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T13:52:42.000Z","msg":"有冇麻友"}]}